Package reports

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Report
    Interface for all reports generated from Fortune 500 data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompanyReport
    A report for a single company of Fortune 500 data.
    YearReport
    A report for a single year of Fortune 500 data.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataNotProcessedException
    An Exception to be thrown if it is attempted to write a report that has not been processed.
    YearNotFoundException
    An Exception to be thrown if a requested year is not present in the data set.
